  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Ed</title>

    <para>Installez <application>Ed</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --bindir=/bin &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Pour tester les résultats, lancez&nbsp;: <command>make check</command>.</para>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Explication des commandes</title>

    <para><parameter>--bindir=/bin</parameter>: This parameter places the
    <command>ed</command> binary into the root filesystem.</para>

  </sect2>

